    • handleAction

      public void handleAction​(PosMessage message)
      This method is used to direct (depending on the current phase) to the correct sub-method to manage correctly the next action

      If the phase is a special one, the method calls the appropriate GodController and launch the special method

      Parameters:
      message - the message arrived from a view

    • handleChooseConstructor

      public void handleChooseConstructor​(PosMessage message)
      This method places the current constructor in the position passed calling the method performChooseConstructor in model
      Parameters:
      message - PosMessage with the position where to place the currentConstructor

    • handleMove

      public void handleMove​(PosMessage message)
      This method calls the performMove method in model. It also checks if the game ends, when the currentConstructor goes up from the second level to the third.
      Parameters:
      message - The positionMessage representing where the player is going to move

    • handleBuild

      public void handleBuild​(PosMessage message)
      This method calls the performBuild in model.
      Parameters:
      message - PosMessage with the position where to build

    • preparePhase

      public void preparePhase()
      This method is used to direct (depending on the current phase) to the correct sub-method to manage correctly the preparation of the next phase

      If the phase is a special one, the method calls the appropriate GodController and launch the special method

    • prepareChooseConstructor

      public void prepareChooseConstructor()
      This method prepares the chooseConstructorPhase. In particular, it checks if the current Player is the last standing and if he is losing. If none of the conditions mentioned before are TRUE, it creates the matrix with all possible constructors.

    • prepareMove

      public void prepareMove()
      This method creates the matrix with all the tiles where the currentConstructor can move.

    • prepareBuild

      public void prepareBuild()
      This method creates the matrix with all the tiles where the currentConstructor can build.

    • executeWinSequence

      public void executeWinSequence()
      This method launches the win sequence, where is declared a winner and the game simply end
